ad secured a restraining order against him for domestic abuse, he had previously violated it.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Henry|first1=Colleen|title=Man threatening wife killed by Milwaukee police Wife had restraining order against Tyrone Ryerson Lawrence|url=http://www.wisn.com/article/man-threatening-wife-killed-by-milwaukee-police/6325775|website=wisn.com|publisher=WISN TV, Milwaukee, Wisconsin|accessdate=26 October 2016|date=6 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Langemo|first1=Laura|last2=Sanchick|first2=Myra|title=\"It\u2019s disturbing:\" 45-year-old man killed in confrontation with Milwaukee police|url=http://fox6now.com/2015/03/06/45-year-old-man-killed-in-confrontation-with-milwaukee-police/|website=fox6now.com|publisher=WITI TV Milwaukee|accessdate=26 October 2016|date=6 March 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015-03-04 || Cruice, Derek (26) || [[Deltona, Florida|Florida (Deltona)]] || Derek Cruice was shot in the face during a drug raid for marijuana, he was unarmed and shirtless.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lehman|first1=Mark|title=Protest held after Volusia deputy shoots, kills man Derek Cruice shot dead as deputies served search warrant in Deltona|url=http://www.clickorlando.com/news/protest-planned-after-volusia-deputy-shoots-kills-man/31647976|accessdate=12 March 2015|agency=WKMG Local 6|publisher=Click Orlando}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015-03-04 || Lao, Carl (28) || [[Stockton, California|California (Stockton)]] || Lao was firing a gun into the air when officers arrived and began exchanging gunfire with him. He died March 27, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fox40.com/2015/03/27/man-shot-in-stockton-officer-involved-shooting-dies/|title=Man Shot in Stockton Officer Involved Shooting Dies|work=FOX40|accessdate=21 April 2015}}</ref> \n|-\n| 2015-03-03 || Metz, Matthew (25) || [[Tempe, Arizona|Arizona (Tempe)]] || Matthew Metz was shot and killed after he stabbed an officer responding to a domestic dispute. The Tempe officers heard screams for help, they were attacked as soon as they 